Paper: hep-th/9605045

Date: 1996-05-07

Title: New equations for vacuum correlators in gauge theories

Authors: D.V.Antonov (ITEP, Moscow)

Comments: 26 pages

Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A11 (1996) 4401-4418

Stochastic quantization is applied to derivation of equations connectingmultilocal gauge-invariant correlators in different field theories. Theyinclude Abelian Higgs Model, QCD with spinless quarks at T=0 and T>0 and QED,where spin effects are taken into account exactly.